                <h1>Alex Kushniarou</h1>
                <h2 class="about" id="about">Aspiring programmer and IT enthusiast</h2>
                <p>Currently, I am a full time web-dev and programmming learner. I chose to follow the path of self-intruction as a first contact with this professional area. I resort mainly to the resources provided by internet-based platforms such as <a href="https://www.udemy.com/" target="_blank">Udemy</a>, <a href="https://www.freecodecamp.org/" target="_blank">FreeCodeCamp</a> and <a href="https://www.codecademy.com/" target="_blank">Codecademy</a>. My first committed contact with this area dates back to Sept. 2019, and so far I have enjoyed every little progress through the journey. The result of my devotion is this "web page" adapted to a form of a CV, which I send you to highlight my most recent and relevant achievements so far.</p>
                <p>Nevertheless, I have a scientific background as you can see below; I majored in Chemistry. My work experience since then is related to that field, although I am very eager to incorporate my gained and improved IT skills into my professional profile as soon as possible. Hence my interest in IRUBIS GmbH at the moment. Thanks for listening to me :)</p>
